  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study wants to prove that SMS monitoring reduced the number of suicide attempts in six
      months according to the beginning of its implementation in the group of the patients
      benefiting SMS compared with the group of patients benefiting from the usual care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
